stream
BT
/F1 11 Tf
72 750 Td
(Target ASIL integrity level: ASIL-B \(ISO 26262\).) Tj
72 736 Td
(The BMS communicates via CAN 2.0B at 500 kbps and CAN-FD at 2 Mbps \(new Rev 2.0\).) Tj
72 722 Td
(Connector standard: 48-pin automotive-grade sealed connector.) Tj
72 708 Td
() Tj
72 694 Td
(3. Functional Requirements) Tj
72 680 Td
(HAG-REQ-F001: The BMS shall monitor individual cell voltages in range 2.5 V to 4.2 V.) Tj
72 666 Td
(  Safety-critical. See FMEA entry F-001 in NOVA-FMEA-004.) Tj
72 652 Td
(HAG-REQ-F002: Cell voltage measurement accuracy shall be within plus or minus 5 mV.) Tj
72 638 Td
(HAG-REQ-F003: The BMS shall monitor pack temperature at a minimum of 8 sensor points.) Tj
72 624 Td
(  Safety-critical. Temperature sensor type: NTC 10k.) Tj
72 610 Td
(HAG-REQ-F004: The BMS shall transmit State-of-Charge \(SOC\) via CAN.) Tj
72 596 Td
(  CAN message ID: 0x1A0. Update rate: 100 ms. Signal definition: see NOVA-IRS-002.) Tj
72 582 Td
(HAG-REQ-F005: The BMS shall detect inter-cell balancing deviation exceeding 50 mV.) Tj
72 568 Td
(  Passive balancing shall activate automatically.) Tj
72 554 Td
(HAG-REQ-F006: Overtemperature protection shall activate at 60 degrees C.) Tj
72 540 Td
(  Safety-critical. Thermal runaway prevention per ISO 26262 clause 5.) Tj
72 526 Td
(HAG-REQ-F007: The BMS shall support ISO 15118 communication for smart charging.) Tj
72 512 Td
(HAG-REQ-F008: State estimation accuracy: SOC plus or minus 2%, SOH plus or minus 4%.) Tj
72 498 Td
(  CHANGED from Rev 1.0: accuracy improved from 3%/5% to 2%/4%.) Tj
72 484 Td
(HAG-REQ-F009: The BMS shall log all fault events to non-volatile memory \(min 2000 events\).) Tj
ET

endstream
